## Leaflet Map Config Field

A field that captures Leaflet map configuration (tile-server URL, attribution, and default zoom / center).

### Usage

```ts
import { CardDef, field, contains } from 'https://cardstack.com/base/card-api';
import LeafletMapConfigField from '@cardstack/catalog/fields/leaflet-map-config-field';

export class Example extends CardDef {
  @field mapConfig = contains(LeafletMapConfigField);
}
```
